name: Beer Night Loop Reversed
description:
Hey June, you are so rad.
Take a hard run, and make it easy.
Remember to let DRA into your heart.
Then you can start, to make runs easy.

IT'S SOCIAL NIGHT.
June will be celebrated with a run then a beer
We head to Celtic Corner post run for our monthly social
As alway we meet at the SPG at 6:30pm!
